              <p class="lead">
                Connect your Google Calendar and let our AI assistant handle all your appointment scheduling needs.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                No more scheduling conflicts, missed appointments, or double bookings. Our system works seamlessly with your existing calendar.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefits mb-4">
              <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="p-3 border rounded h-100">
