                    </svg>
                    <h5>Automatic Scheduling</h5>
                    <p class="small">Appointments are automatically added to your calendar as clients book them.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="p-3 border rounded h-100">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-phone mb-3 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
